</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_war\" title=\"Shadow war\">Shadow war</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Yunkish Campaign</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_the_Horns_of_Hazzat\" title=\"Battle at the Horns of Hazzat\">Horns of Hazzat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Fighting_on_the_Khyzai_Pass\" title=\"Fighting on the Khyzai Pass\">Khyzai Pass</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Siege of Astapor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Second_siege_of_Meereen\" title=\"Second siege of Meereen\">Second siege of Meereen</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403193401\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.110 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.259 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2489/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 17236/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 26120/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 4194/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 7682/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.130/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.44 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  234.160      1 -total\n 78.88%  184.703      1 Template:Battlebox\n 78.55%  183.927      1 Template:Infobox\n 14.16%   33.149     24 Template:Ref\n  8.38%   19.616     24 Template:Ref/core\n  3.94%    9.223      1 Template:Targaryen_campaign_in_Slavers_Bay\n  3.68%    8.620      1 Template:Navbox\n  3.50%    8.193      5 Template:Quote\n  3.18%    7.457      1 Template:Date\n  1.77%    4.143      1 Template:Navbar